{"tid":2289021,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[零售撚入] 遲左7分鐘on floor，第2日收警告信，點睇??","createTime":"2020-11-17T03:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T03:02:29.000Z","uid":335222,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcd42afb1fb5ecd9956701bad4d1c89014bf6b6","tid":2289021,"uid":335222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"借朋友account開post<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n本人第一次返零售業，而家係外國Lululexxx做緊part-time educator，返左個零月，無遲到過，遇到個咁既manager(有圖thanks)，想問下巴絲們是咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說果日返2點，我2點正返到去clock in，但因為19武漢肺炎要填健康申報表，而果日部電腦又神神地，所以搞多左陣。臨出去之前撞到個manager，佢問我咩事遲(07分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，我就話地鐵同電腦有問題。Manager冇特別鳩地叫我下次唔好，但係第2日就收到呢封email鳥(cc埋其他senior/key leader)。<br />\n<br />\n零售撚們點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿屌老母:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeffb02d748852148bab60f7a813ff28b3cfe0e0","tid":2289021,"uid":35746,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"一係做 一係唔做，有咩點睇？"},{"pid":"92147226d0e15ecfe8d5d1202d3e9778cc1b2d0d","tid":2289021,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"then come early and leave sharp on time."},{"pid":"fc2ba35c9d78ea37d14470271b88670e17c21b34","tid":2289021,"uid":335222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeffb02d748852148bab60f7a813ff28b3cfe0e0","tid":2289021,"uid":35746,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"一係做 一係唔做，有咩點睇？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"純粹想知下零售業既文化是咪咁，定係因公司/人而異<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396cb53a04e825d0d48f23f4d4b3270ad6e0540d","tid":2289021,"uid":163193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc